  "title": "logistic manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and implement strategies to optimize the supply chain, transportation, and distribution in Singapore.</li><li>Oversee entire logistics operations.</li><li>Resolve logistics issues such as delays, damages, or documentation errors while driving process improvements to enhance accuracy and efficiency.</li><li>Act as key logistics focal for any customer deliveries query and escalations for parts availability.</li><li>Drive ongoing process improvements and operational efficiency initiatives to strengthen logistics performance.</li><li>Establish and maintain relationships with suppliers, factories and customers to ensure reliable and cost-effective transportation of goods in timely manner.</li><li>Apply logistics expertise to support cross-border operations and complex supply chain activities.   </li><li>Track and analyze key performance indicators (KPIs) to identify areas for improvement and implement corrective actions.</li><li>Supervise and mentor logistics staff, fostering a positive and productive work environment, and ensuring that the team is well-trained and equipped to handle the logistics operations.</li><li>Experience in leading a logistics team and to improve logistics supply chain efficiency.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Bachelor’s degree in Logistics and Supply Chain Management, or equivalent qualification.</li><li>Proven background in logistics or warehouse operations, coupled with strong leadership experience.</li><li>At least four years of relevant experience in logistics or supply chain.</li><li>Proven ability to oversee 3PL providers and handle multi-channel logistics</li><li>Strong communication skills and exceptional stakeholder management capabilities.</li><li>Effective in managing people, with previous or ongoing leadership experience considered an advantage.</li><li>Proficient in multitasking in a fast-paced environment.</li><li>Comfortable handling challenging or high-stress situations.</li><li>Holds a valid Class 3 driving license</li></ul>",
